Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Russians win US grain deal
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z9200
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 26 Oct 1975
Soviets to buy US grain in new deal - but China signals fears over detente. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.